Privacy Policy — Unit Converter: Simple & Fast

Last updated: May 12, 2026

Overview

Unit Converter: Simple & Fast is a fully offline app. It does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data — ever.

Data Collection

We collect no data of any kind. This includes:

No personal information
No usage statistics or analytics
No crash reports sent to any server
No device identifiers
No location data
Internet Access

This app requires no internet connection and requests no network permissions. It works entirely on your device.

Third-Party Services

This app uses no third-party SDKs, advertising networks, or analytics services.

Data Storage

The only data stored on your device is your last-used unit selections, saved locally by the Android operating system. This data never leaves your device and can be cleared at any time by uninstalling the app.

Children's Privacy

This app is safe for users of all ages. No data is collected from anyone, including children under the age of 13.

Changes to This Policy

If a future update introduces any data collection, this policy will be updated before that version is released.

